      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen is mechanically superlative: the dual-VANOS system has been fully overhauled, and the rod bearing service is documented. The chassis is structurally optimized with a reinforced rear subframe. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory variable M differential lock. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing sharp turn-in and exceptional lateral grip. Finished in pristine Laguna Seca Blue with original paint depth verified across all panels, this vehicle represents a turnkey investment for the discerning collector.",
