      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that defines the 'mint' standard. This car has been meticulously garage-kept and professionally detailed, featuring a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero rock chips or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, smelling fresh and showing absolutely no wear on the premium leather seating or touchpoints. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history and a recent multi-point inspection confirming peak performance. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the lot. Includes both original keys, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning buyer to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives like new.",
